{
  "info": {
    "name": "Gopher - Go Minimal Backend",
    "description": "รวม endpoint ทั้งหมดของ Go Minimal Backend template ไว้ทดสอบผ่าน Postman ได้ทันที\n\nวิธีใช้:\n1. Import ไฟล์นี้เข้า Postman (Import > เลือกไฟล์นี้)\n2. เช็คว่า server รันอยู่แล้ว (`go run cmd/api/main.go` หรือ `docker compose up -d --build`)\n3. ยิง Auth > Login (Admin) หรือ Login (New User) ก่อน — token จะถูกเก็บลง collection variable `token` ให้อัตโนมัติผ่าน test script ข้างใน\n4. ยิง request อื่นๆ ต่อได้เลย มันจะแนบ `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}` ให้เองทุกครั้ง",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:5000" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "note_id", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register (New User)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"testuser\",\n  \"password\": \"test1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "register"] },
            "description": "สมัคร user ใหม่ (ได้ role \"user\" เสมอ) — 201 = สำเร็จ, 409 = username ซ้ำ"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (New User)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('token saved:', body.token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"testuser\",\n  \"password\": \"test1234\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "description": "Login ด้วย user ธรรมดา (ต้อง Register ก่อน) — ได้ role \"user\" ทำได้ทุกอย่างยกเว้น Delete note"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Admin - seeded)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "    console.log('admin token saved:', body.token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"golang123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "auth", "login"] },
            "description": "Login ด้วย admin ที่ระบบ seed ให้อัตโนมัติตอน boot ครั้งแรก (username: admin, password: golang123) — role \"admin\" เท่านั้นที่ Delete note ได้"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Notes",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Notes",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/notes", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "notes"] },
            "description": "ดึงโน้ตทั้งหมดของ user ที่ login อยู่ (ต้องมี token)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Note",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('note_id', body.id);",
                  "    console.log('note_id saved:', body.id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"My first note\",\n  \"content\": \"Hello world\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/notes", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "notes"] },
            "description": "สร้างโน้ตใหม่ — id ที่ได้จะถูกเก็บลง note_id ให้อัตโนมัติ เอาไปใช้กับ Get/Update/Delete ต่อได้เลย\n\nลองส่ง title ว่างดูจะได้ 400 พร้อม error รายฟิลด์ (validation)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Note By ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/notes/{{note_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "notes", "{{note_id}}"] },
            "description": "ดึงโน้ต 1 อันด้วย id (ใช้ note_id ที่ได้จาก Create Note) — ดึงโน้ตของ user คนอื่นจะได้ 404 เสมอ"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Note",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"Updated title\",\n  \"content\": \"Updated content\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/notes/{{note_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "notes", "{{note_id}}"] },
            "description": "แก้ไขโน้ต (ต้องเป็นเจ้าของเท่านั้น)"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Note (Admin only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/notes/{{note_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "notes", "{{note_id}}"] },
            "description": "ลบโน้ต — ต้อง login ด้วย admin เท่านั้น (ยิงด้วย token ของ user ธรรมดาจะได้ 403 Forbidden)"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
